<tr id="L43"><td><a href="#L43">43</a></td><td>PRESSMAN:  As you know, the starship Pegasus was lost in this sector some twelve years ago along with most of its crew. I was the captain and Commander Riker here was my helmsman.</td></tr>

<tr id="L44"><td><a href="#L44">44</a></td><td>PICARD:  I remember hearing about it. The ship was destroyed by a warp core breach as I recall.</td></tr>

