<tr id="L298"><td><a href="#L298">298</a></td><td>RIKER:  And now you want to try it again? How many people will die this time? Fifty? A hundred? A thousand?</td></tr>

<tr id="L299"><td><a href="#L299">299</a></td><td>PRESSMAN:  All right, you don't want to help me? Fine. But you are still under my direct orders not to talk about what you know and I expect you to follow those orders to the letter. I made you, mister, and I can break you just as easily. Do you understand me, Commander?</td></tr>

