<tr id="L312"><td><a href="#L312">312</a></td><td>SIROL [on viewscreen]:  I'm not sure. We were conducting some geological experiments on the surface of the asteroid. It is entirely possible that we accidently sealed you in. If only we had known you were beneath the surface, if you had shared your plans with us, this might have been avoided.</td></tr>

