<tr id="L324"><td><a href="#L324">324</a></td><td>RIKER:  Captain, I have a suggestion. There's a piece of equipment in Admiral Pressman's quarters under guard which might get us out of here. It's a prototype for a Federation cloaking device.</td></tr>

